<bibRefCitation id="EFD34B2486026B24F9D089CFF859FA79" author="Campbell, K. S. W. &amp; B. Engel" box="[1544,1987,1467,1506]" pageId="16" pageNumber="79" pagination="55 - 122" refId="ref24605" refString="Campbell, K. S. W. &amp; B. Engel, 1963. The Faunas of the Tournaisian Tulcumba Sandstone and its Members in the Werrie and Belvue Synclines, N. S. W. Geological Society of Australia Journal 10 (1): 55 - 122." type="journal article" year="1963">Campbell &amp; Engel, 1963</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
